    &quot;Parasite&quot; - &quot;Ladies in Waiting&quot; replaces &quot;Parasite&quot; on shows up to 1/25/1976 in Detroit
    &quot;Nothin' to Lose&quot;
    &quot;100,000 Years&quot; (Gene Simmons bass solo, Peter Criss drum solo)
    &quot;Black Diamond&quot;
